    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Unique Mixed-Genre Experience that feels Vibrant, Whimsical, and Refreshing! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go haywire and become the world's most mischievous vacuum cleaner!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What You'll Do:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLEAN  </strong><br>Vacuum trash, smash objects, and overachieve by clearing every corner of the levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COLLECT</strong><br>Every object and hidden collectible sucked up or disposed appears in the player's home </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONQUER </strong><br> Tackle sandbox stages with evolving challenges and unlock bonus levels each with their own special twist</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333940/extras/d7cf8e16e033b753591d66b6a7582b65.poster.avif?t=1760750575\" width=338 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333940/extras/d7cf8e16e033b753591d66b6a7582b65.webm?t=1760750575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333940/extras/d7cf8e16e033b753591d66b6a7582b65.mp4?t=1760750575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why ACUVAC Stands Out:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consistent, immersive controls that teach themselves, rich content, and a brand-new spin on cleaning chaos that’s as satisfying as it is ridiculous.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approach cleaning levels and special objectives your own way. With playable arcade machines, and even boss fights, you'll encounter the unexpected as a vacuum cleaner!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333940/extras/67e7d2f450d00d21748b4c27cef8dc60.poster.avif?t=1760750575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333940/extras/67e7d2f450d00d21748b4c27cef8dc60.webm?t=1760750575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333940/extras/67e7d2f450d00d21748b4c27cef8dc60.mp4?t=1760750575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Inspired By Classics:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Katamari Damacy</strong> <br>Engage in playful and satisfying physics-driven object collection where <u>every object is collectible or disposable!</u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luigi’s Mansion</strong> <br>Use powerful suction  mechanics used to uncover secrets and gobble up everything.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Octodad </strong> <br>Master physically interacting limb controls that let you use your hose in fun, silly, and memorable ways</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get It Today!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience one of the most creative, chaotic, and satisfying physics-based adventures. <strong>Buy ACUVAC: A Suck and Blow Adventure</strong> and get ready to turn cleaning into chaos!   </p>",
